data.title: Petty Officer Second Class John F Doyle
data.meta_description: Online plaque dedicated to Petty Officer Second Class John F Doyle. Mt. Soledad National Veterans Memorial.
data.text:
Boatswain's Mate Second Class

MEDALS-RIBBONS: Purple Heart, Presidential Unit Citation, Navy Good Conduct, American Campaign, European-African-Middle Eastern Campaign w/1 Star, Asiatic Pacific Campaign w/1 Silver and 1 Bronze Star, World War lI Victory

PUC aboard Dallas during Operation "Torch". Transferred to Hutchins and Pacific Theater for remainder of WWII Shellback aboard Hutchins.
